             was a second time indicted for <rs id="t17730421-29-off167" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17730421-29-off167" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17730421-29-off167" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               that he on the king's highway, on 
                     
                        <persName id="t17730421-29-victim407" type="victimName">
                           Henry
                            Cothery
                        <interp inst="t17730421-29-victim407" type="surname" value="Cothery"></interp>
